column5: Does anyone know if Basskicker is still around, Jason?  Or did I write his name down wrong?  He will have a print coming at the end of July if I can find him.  Pam
Pamela....if you need to get a message for him, I can give him a call...just let me know.  He is still around on the board with that name.  Cliff
There is a Bass Killer but not basskicker on board.  Maybe he changed it?  Thanks Cliff.  Pam
We were wondering the same thing aboot you Pam!
I've left him a message for you Pam...Sinker found his profile at any rate.
